name: Archives - 02 - Anonymous photographer in Hackney, London, on 19/09/2004
description: Photo taken on September 19th 2004 in London during the “Shoreditch Festival and Car Free Day”. Several physical copies of this, printed on paper but on a smaller scale, existed as an invitation to the solo exhibition “Strike a Pose”, which happened from 29/09/2005 to 04/10/2005 in Milan, Italy: probably none of them survived to the current date. Shot with a Sony DSC-T1 pocket-sized camera by Matteo Manzini @matteomanzini__ (Twitter/Instagram).
